										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure id="attachment_18606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-18606" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-18606" src="https://www.shl-tech.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/SHL-Technologies-at-2023-Taiwan-Automation-Intelligence-and-Robotic-Show.jpg" alt="Banner of SHL Technologies announcing its participation for the first time at 2023 Taiwan Automation Intelligence and Robotic Show. It will exhibit at Booth #N1206 from Aug 23-26." width="1920" height="630"><figcaption id="caption-attachment-18606" class="wp-caption-text">SHL Technologies will showcase its comprehensive manufacturing capabilities and expertise at Automation Taipei 2023.</figcaption></figure>



<p>SHL Technologies, a contract manufacturer and original equipment manufacturer (OEM), announced its first-ever participation at the 2023 Taiwan Automation Intelligence and Robot Show. The exhibition will be held on August 23-26 at Taipei Nangang Exhibition Center Hall 1 &#8211; 4F, where SHL Technologies will be exhibiting at Booth #N1206.</p>



<p>The Taiwan Automation Intelligence and Robot Show is an annual exhibition, which gathers various industry professionals in the field of manufacturing, artificial intelligence, and robotics. The exhibition serves as an ideal platform to encourage communications and expand discussions around the myriad manufacturing applications in the industrial, science, and healthcare industries.&nbsp;</p>



<p>SHL Technologies will demonstrate its industry knowledge, cutting-edge technologies, and customer-centric approach to project planning and execution to provide forward-thinking solutions that offer real value to our partners. With a remarkable wealth of industry experience, SHL Technologies is excited to engage with other industry professionals and stakeholders, build meaningful connections, and explore new business opportunities.</p>



<p>As subsidiary of <a href="https://www.shl-medical.com/">SHL Medical</a>, SHL Technologies provides high-quality manufacturing and engineering solutions for medtech and other industrial sectors. Backed by its comprehensive, in-house <a href="https://www.shl-tech.com/expertise/">expertise</a> and <a href="https://www.shl-tech.com/capabilities/">capabilities</a>, SHL Technologies is able to provide a tailored approach to support its partners through the project lifecycle. From project feasibility, resources management, quality execution, to cost-reduction identification, SHL Technologies proactively strives to meet its partners wherever they are in the development process.</p>



<p>Visitors to the booth will have the opportunity to meet in-person with our experts to gain firsthand knowledge about SHL Technologies’ <a href="https://www.shl-tech.com/solutions/">solutions and projects</a>, discover how SHL Technologies can address their needs and support their businesses, as well as discuss potential strategic partnerships.</p>



