<p>SHL Technologies launches a brand new official website at <a href="http://www.shl-tech.com">www.shl-tech.com</a>. The new website capitalizes on SHL Technologies&#8217; unique characteristics and offerings. Rooted in the SHL legacy, this separate brand identity signifies SHL Technologies&#8217; dedication to its customers by providing more insightful knowledge on its expertise and capabilities.</p>
